Valentine’s Day is fast approaching – but with the UK still in lockdown, a romantic meal out is off the table. What better time, then, to get cosy with your favourite romcom? Whether it’s a film or TV show, a golden oldie or a recent release, we want to hear about the romcoms that you return to, time and again. You can get in touch by filling in the form below, anonymously if you wish. Your responses are secure as the form is encrypted and only the Guardian has access to your contributions. One of our journalists will be in contact before we publish, so please do leave contact details. If you’re having trouble using the form, click here. Read terms of service here.